cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.IT, cs.NA, cs.MM

The paper proposes a method for image reconstruction using a data-driven approach inspired by deep learning. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) or machine learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. The method also involves optimization techniques, which could place it in the information theory (cs.IT) or numerical analysis (cs.NA) sub-categories. Finally, the paper applies the proposed method to the problem of deconvolution in a fluorescence microscope, which suggests that it could also belong to the multimedia (cs.MM) sub-category.
